 Customer Segmentation Project

 Project Overview

This project focuses on segmenting customers based on their behavior and demographic characteristics. Customer segmentation helps businesses understand different customer groups and develop targeted marketing strategies.

 Objectives

* Analyze customer behavior and demographics.
* Identify customer segments using clustering techniques.
* Understand purchasing patterns and preferences.
* Visualize customer groups and their characteristics.

 Key Features

* Customer data analysis.
* Customer clustering using machine learning techniques.
* Visualization of customer segments.
* Identification of purchasing trends.
* Customer insights generation.

Tools Used

* Python (Scikit-learn)
* Pandas
* Matplotlib
* Power BI (Optional)

Methodology

1. Collect customer data.
2. Clean and preprocess the dataset.
3. Select important features.
4. Apply clustering algorithms such as K-Means.
5. Visualize customer segments.
6. Interpret customer behavior patterns.

 Expected Outcome

The project provides insights into customer groups, purchasing behavior, and targeted business opportunities.

## Conclusion

Customer segmentation helps organizations improve marketing strategies, enhance customer experience, and increase business growth through data-driven decisions.
